=== 造型艺术 ===
[[file:20160621_102725_resized.jpg|thumb]]
19世纪，蒙梭罗城堡吸引了一批[[浪漫主义|浪漫主义]]和前印象主义艺术家前往卢瓦尔河谷旅游。
1832年，[[约瑟夫·玛罗德·威廉·特纳|透纳]]在他游历卢瓦尔河谷德旅途中绘下了一幅卢瓦尔河与维埃纳河汇流的水彩画（现藏于[[牛津|牛津]][[阿什莫林博物馆|阿什莫林博物馆]]）。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.tate.org.uk/art/artworks/turner-rietz-near-saumur-engraved-by-r-brandard-t04690|title=‘Rietz, near Saumur, engraved by R. Brandard’, after Joseph Mallord William Turner, 1832 {{!}} Tate|last=Tate|work=Tate Etc.|access-date=13 October 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.tate.org.uk/art/artworks/turner-rietz-near-saumur-tw0725|title=‘Rietz, near Saumur’, Joseph Mallord William Turner, c.1826–30 {{!}} Tate|last=Tate|work=Tate Etc.|access-date=13 October 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402073341/https://www.tate.org.uk/art/artworks/turner-rietz-near-saumur-tw0725|archive-date=2019-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 1897年前后，[[奥古斯特·罗丹|奥古斯特·罗丹]]绘下了一幅建筑北侧的素描。

